1
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:29,480
What's wrong?

2
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:32,400
Am I disturbing you this late?

3
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:41,370
Happy birthday.

4
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:44,040
Did you set all this up?

5
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:45,320
Make a wish.

6
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:47,320
Mhm.

7
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:51,800
I hope this happy time

8
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:53,600
can last forever.

9
00:00:58,440 --> 00:00:59,240
This is a gift.

10
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:01,200
Here.

11
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:02,280
Thank you.

12
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,660
Let me put it on for you.

13
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:39,600
Does it look good?

14
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,979
What are you doing?

15
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,289
Symmetry looks better.

16
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,920
Just you wait.

17
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,810
What's wrong, Mr. Wang?

18
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,320
Yufan, come to school right now.

19
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,320
So urgent?

20
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:52,600
Special circumstances. We'll talk when you get here.

21
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,200
Mr. Wang.

22
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:57,329
Why did you call me here in such a hurry?

23
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,600
It's the principal.

24
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:00,080
He wants to see you tomorrow morning.

25
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,680
I was really worried, so I contacted you first.

26
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,080
The principal wants to see me?

27
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:04,560
Yes.

28
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,120
Right now, at the school gate,

29
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:08,400
there's a group of people waiting for you, trying to collect debts.

30
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,440
You know about this, right?

31
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,240
Yes.

32
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,240
The principal is also worried.

33
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,160
He's afraid that

34
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,280
if they run into you

35
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,530
and make a big scene,

36
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,600
you might be in danger.

37
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,399
So,

38
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,240
he wants you to

39
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,410
take a leave of absence for a while.

40
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,000
So fast?

41
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,460
This is too sudden.

42
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,000
There's no other way.

43
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,960
The principal has to consider

44
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,690
the safety of all the students.

45
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:37,240
Then why did you ask to see me alone?

46
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,720
I think

47
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,360
you should insist on not taking a leave of absence.

48
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,440
At least,

49
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,280
hold on for another week.

50
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,720
Look,

51
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,880
do you remember this document?

52
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,560
Why are you here?

53
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:21,600
Are you cold?

54
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,920
How did it go?

55
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,240
The teacher was in such a hurry.

56
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,040
It must be something important.

57
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,040
Yeah.

58
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:31,400
I might have to leave school for a while.

59
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,720
Why is that?

60
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,480
Someone leaked my information.

61
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,920
Now people come to the school gate to block me every day.

62
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,380
It's all because of my dad's corporate debt.

63
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,640
But that's not your problem.

64
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:46,840
But the school needs to ensure the safety of every student.

65
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:48,200
I will be back soon.

66
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,320
I close my eyes,

67
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:25,180
listening to your heartbeat and breathing.

68
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:28,040
And at this moment, only we are left on Earth.

69
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,500
The shape of your smiling lips

70
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,320
always captivates my heart.

71
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,280
Principal.

72
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:58,920
Mr. Wang.

73
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,050
I brought him to you.

74
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:01,640
Come, take a seat.

75
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:08,410
Mr. Wang should have told you my thoughts.

76
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:09,840
He did.

77
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:12,080
He wants me to take a leave of absence.

78
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:12,840
The school

79
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:15,240
is considering the safety of you students.

80
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,800
We hope you can understand.

81
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,640
Principal, how about this?

82
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,120
Let Yufan

83
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,050
assist me first.

84
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,280
Once this campus loan sharking issue

85
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:25,040
is cleared up, he can take his leave of absence.

86
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:27,320
The investigation is the school's responsibility.

87
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,760
How can we let a student get involved?

88
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:30,840
I know, but right now,

89
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:33,280
this matter involves too many students.

90
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,850
Many are even connected to the student union.

91
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:38,010
We also need Yufan's help for this.

92
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,860
Can you give me three days?

93
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,040
I'll find the evidence within three days

94
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,120
and catch the mastermind.

95
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:46,520
Three days? Yufan, this is too risky.

96
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,280
Are you sure?

97
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,900
Are three days enough?

98
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,170
The school will fully support you.

99
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:55,060
For these three days, cooperate well with Mr. Wang's investigation.

100
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,360
Casting Associate Director: Xi Chongjing

101
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,280
Props Assistant: Li Kunxiao

102
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:09,200
Unit Vehicle: Yi Mingle

103
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:11,160
Yitong
